{"tid":2141943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"研發芯片恐燒錢千億","createTime":"2020-08-06T05:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T05:31:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8685ba31476510d9e7f78db21f149f0924c96659","tid":2141943,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:24:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/RMVTXB2MUNAZUM2DHVJHP4U4YE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2FRMVTXB2MUNAZUM2DHVJHP4U4YE%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=24508431\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2FRMVTXB2MUNAZUM2DHVJHP4U4YE%2F&h=a1e4bdb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/RMVTXB2MUNAZUM2DHVJHP4U4YE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n研發芯片恐燒錢千億<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RoZnnhumhn5YE9TTasg089JpP2E=/400x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MRYYIAL3TXTIF7MAC2PVTV2XGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRoZnnhumhn5YE9TTasg089JpP2E%3D%2F400x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMRYYIAL3TXTIF7MAC2PVTV2XGU.jpg&h=354a2f34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地晶片龍頭中芯只可量產12納米晶片，而台積電已在量產7納米晶片。<br />\n<br />\n美國封殺中國高科技發展，市場最多談論箝制中國晶片，即內地稱為芯片的出口，不少行內人已指中國要以年計去追上龍頭台積電的水平；其實耗上的不止是時間，更要燒上千億元計去研發。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：天災或釀糧食危機  洪水、蝗禍摧毀經濟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台積電「贏者通吃」<br />\n<br />\n目前內地晶片龍頭中芯的技術，只可量產12納米晶片，而台積電已在量產7納米晶片，5納米晶片亦將在今年量產。科大教授李貽昆指，要開發晶片的資金達百億美元計，為量產7納米晶片，台積電投放高達180億美元。目前台積電已霸佔了這個市場，連華為5G基站亦是採用台積電代工的7納米晶片。<br />\n<br />\n台積電市佔率高達五成，令。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n晶片市場不單是贏者通吃，更。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，即使晶片大小相同，李。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"21ee236a8a74f797c0e0e20b4752b910ac43d522","tid":2141943,"uid":251009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:30:59.000Z","msg":"新太空競賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c624510365da2bd66dc17467eea80e82e269d07","tid":2141943,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"蘇聯下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}